议定稿；18/19/20 过期表述回写\\n  · 引擎 R [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":49,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-20236fe2-44de-47d4-86b9-ae1d994e647c-6\\nfc_c9658bc1-1c3a-994e-877f-eabe6d67a92c_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"node:fs|better-sqlite3|readFileSync|writeFileSync|fs\\\\.|sqlite|createSqlite|@deprecated|兼容转发|已迁至\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"call-20236fe2-44de-47d4-86b9-ae1d994e647c-6\\nfc_c9658bc1-1c3a-994e-877f-eabe6d67a92c_1\",\"offset\":0}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-20236fe2-44de-47d4-86b9-ae1d994e647c-6\\nfc_c9658bc1-1c3a-994e-877f-eabe6d67a92c_1\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784786677785\"},\"model_call_id\":\"7e00fda9-003f-4713-bb4d-dd6638a4a66f-2-cjy5\",\"session_id\":\"ba9f1f4a-8af3-41d1-9254-1eee7937ded0\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784786677718}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":51,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-20236fe2-44de-47d4-86b9-ae1d994e647c-6\\nfc_c9658bc1-1c3a-994e-877f-eabe6d67a92c_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"node:fs|better-sqlite3|readFileSync|writeFileSync|fs\\\\.|sqlite|createSqlite|@deprecated|兼容转发|已迁至\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"call-20236fe2-44de-47d4-86b9-ae1d994e647c-6\\nfc_c9658bc1-1c3a-994e-877f-eabe6d67a92c_1\",\"offset\":0},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"pattern\":\"node:fs|better-sqlite3|readFileSync|writeFileSync|fs\\\\.|sqlite|createSqlite|@deprecated|兼容转发|已迁至\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine\",\"outputMode\":\"content\",\"workspaceResults\":{\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\":{\"content\":{\"matches\":[{\"file\":\"packages/rpg-engin