{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-0eafe894-92e0-4145-9df7-50adcc4b9546-27\nfc_1cd03b53-a562-9c48-b598-53597833ab1b_6","tool_call":{"grepToolCall":{"args":{"pattern":"engineIOModule|Port|存取","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档","glob":"{18,19,20,23}*.md","caseInsensitive":false,"headLimit":40,"multiline":false,"toolCallId":"call-0eafe894-92e0-4145-9df7-50adcc4b9546-27\nfc_1cd03b53-a562-9c48-b598-53597833ab1b_6","offset":0},"result":{"success":{"pattern":"engineIOModule|Port|存取","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档","outputMode":"content","workspaceResults":{"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine":{"content":{"matches":[{"file":"docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":1,"content":"# 23. 引擎存取 Port 与 IO 适配","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":3,"content":"相关：[18](./18-部署拓扑与BS架构.md) · [19](./19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) · [20](./20-记忆存储与投影.md) · [里程碑需求](../里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_需求.md) · [引擎使用说明](../../../packages/rpg-engine/README.md)","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":6,"content":"> **一句话：** 引擎只声明「要什么 / 存什么」的 Port 协议；具体落盘由外部 IO 模块响应。本机默认实现物理落在 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":16,"content":"| Studio V2 / 本机 Next | `engineIOModule`：JSON+fs + SQLite + jsonl |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":20,"content":"存储方案随平台变；**剧情与会话规则不变**。故：程序上 Port 化，物理上 IO 实现离开 `packages/rpg-engine`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":30,"content":"  ↓ 装配：createEngineIOPorts(dataRoot) → createEngineHost({ ports })","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":31,"content":"packages/rpg-engine（纯逻辑 + Port 接口）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":32,"content":"  ↕ callback / Port 协议（本文）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":33,"content":"apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/（本机 IO 实现）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":38,"content":"- **引擎禁止** import `engineIOModule` 或 `node:fs` / `better-sqlite3` **实现**。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":39,"content":"- **Client 禁止** import `engineIOModule`（与 Client/Server 隔离规则一致）。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":46,"content":"1. **引擎暴露**一组 Port（存/取 callback）+ **固定**入参/出参形状。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":49,"content":"4. **幂等**：同一 Profile/Content 键重复写，语义由各 Port 方法注释钉死（v1：整文件覆盖写 Profile）。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":50,"content":"5. **类型真源**：Port 接口与 DTO 定义在 `packages/rpg-engine`；`engineIOModule` 可 import 引擎类型，反向禁止。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":56,"content":"## 4. Port 契约（入参 / 出参 · 实现合同）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":64,"content":"### 4.1 MemoryPort","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":67,"content":"**本机实现：** SQLite（原 `createSqliteMemoryPort` → `engineIOModule/memory`）。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":71,"content":"interface MemoryPort {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":125,"content":"### 4.2 ProfilePort","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":132,"content":"interface ProfilePort {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":169,"content":"**实现注意：** 引擎 Host **不得**再拼 `users/.../profile.save.json`；只调本 Port。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":173,"content":"### 4.3 ContentPort","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":176,"content":"**不负责：** Studio 画布 layout 编辑写盘、资源二进制上传（可仍走 BFF）；但 validate 需要的 **读** 必须能经本 Port 完成。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":196,"content":"interface ContentPort {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":227,"content":"   * 缺 conf：仍返回结构，由引擎规则报 SCHEMA / missing（或 Port 直接在 conf 位给 null）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":287,"content":"### 4.4 EngineLogPort","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":289,"content":"**职责：** 引擎旁路日志落盘与切片读（WET 内存 ring 仍可在 Host；**持久化**只经本 Port）。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":294,"content":"interface EngineLogPort {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":324,"content":"**实现注意：** 一行一条 JSON；追加失败不得拖垮通话主路径（Host 可 `.catch` 吞掉，但 Port 本身应如实 throw 或由 Host 包装）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":328,"content":"### 4.5 四 Port 对照总表","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":330,"content":"| Port | 读 | 写 | 空/缺省语义 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":334,"content":"| Content | snapshot / card / conf / validate bundle / asset* | （运行时 Port **无写**；编辑写盘走 BFF） | 缺→null / false |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":343,"content":"  memory?: MemoryPort | null,","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":344,"content":"  profile: ProfilePort,","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":345,"content":"  content: ContentPort,","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":346,"content":"  engineLog?: EngineLogPort,","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":351,"content":"- **测试：** 注入内存假 Port。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":352,"content":"- **本机 Studio：** `engineIOModule` 工厂一次创建全套并注入。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":353,"content":"- **禁止**引擎在未注入时偷偷建 sqlite/fs 实现；默认硬实现已删，本机真源仅 `engineIOModule`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":357,"content":"## 6. `engineIOModule` 物理约定","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":94,"totalMatchedLines":94,"clientTruncated":true,"ripgrepTruncated":false,"headLimitApplied":40}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-0eafe894-92e0-4145-9df7-50adcc4b9546-27\nfc_1cd03b53-a562-9c48-b598-53597833ab1b_6","startedAtMs":"1784786945378","completedAtMs":"1784786945597"},"model_call_id":"fe492f5f-8dfd-4ffd-a499-712723498472-5-gasp","session_id":"c3fe8768-d570-480b-9faf-6afad14b69df","timestamp_ms":1784786945747}
